definition: more than ten/a dozen or more
to count/to count as/to regard as/to enumerate (sb's shortcomings)

sentences.english: Walk along Tung Choi Street and turn left into Bute Street and then turn right into Fa Yuen Street.
sentences.chinese: 沿通菜街走，左轉入弼街，再走十數步便抵達花園街。

sentences.english: The village of white fruit shall have a hundred years of history, more than ten people to come around.
sentences.chinese: 村口的白果樹應有百年曆史，十數人才能圍過來。

sentences.english: As for the billion people in-between the coast and the Tibetan plateau?
sentences.chinese: 那麼在沿海地區與青藏高原之間十數億的人們呢？

sentences.english: Master the method of doing addition and subtraction.
sentences.chinese: 掌握整十數加減法的計算方法。
